## This action will scale glyphs that have been 
## transferred from a 1000 em unit font to a
## 2048 em unit font.
##-----------------------------------------------------
##
set F1 aw            
set F2 lsb  
set F3 [100*2048/1000]
origin 0 0
stretch F3 F3
set lsb [F2*2048/1000]
set aw [F1*2048/1000]
##
##-----------------------------------------------------
